1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:06,500
AgentOps Mobile Command Center is a Telegram-first AI ops console
for mobile founders and operators.

2
00:00:06,500 --> 00:00:13,500
Open the dashboard to see recent runs, approvals, storage health,
and the live demo smoke-test button.

3
00:00:13,500 --> 00:00:20,500
The live route is backed by Fireworks and returns live=true,
so you can verify the demo path on the spot.

4
00:00:20,500 --> 00:00:27,000
From mobile, you can review pull requests, check status,
and approve the next step.
